== Looking for the original Hoppou avatar author ==

Hello, I'm looking for the name of the original author that originally uploaded the first Hoppou Avatar in VRChat.

If you think you know it, we can start a discussion about it here and add it to the avatar infobox description. [[User:Usr 80e15713-9a01-457f-9ab6-72d9ebcb21a2|Usr 80e15713-9a01-457f-9ab6-72d9ebcb21a2]] ([[User talk:Usr 80e15713-9a01-457f-9ab6-72d9ebcb21a2|talk]]) 17:14, 10 October 2024 (UTC)

:The creator of the Northern Princess MMD fan model that would eventually become known as "hoppou" through VRchat was created by Aoi Omoti and originally via bowloroll.net around September 2014 https://bowlroll.net/file/50798  Aoi would also go on to create many other MMD fan models from the KanColle collection often used as the basis of Hoppou related avatars in VRchat : https://bowlroll.net/user/369/files
:In June 2021 Aoi, via their official blog, would clarify the TOS of their MMD models which included NO USE in VRchat : https://aoiomoti.hatenablog.com/entry/2021/06/14/210220
